text: Mindyak () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Mindyaksky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 2,282 as of 2010. There are 56 streets. == Geography == It is located 75 km from Uchaly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Mindyak
